text: Mahender Singh Tawar (Born 3 June 1988) is an Indian Administrative Service (IAS) officer currently serving as the District Magistrate and Collector in Kushinagar. == Career highlights == * Assistant Magistrate/Assistant Collector, Bahraich (May 4, 2016, to September 29, 2017) * Joint Magistrate, Etah (September 30, 2017, to February 12, 2019) == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Indian civil servants Category:People from Uttar Pradesh
title: Mahender Singh Tawar
